<TEXT>
<P>
CRETE, Greece, May 31 (Xinhua) -- Li Ruihuan, chairman of the
National Committee of the Chinese People's Political Consultative
Conference (CPPCC), arrived here from Portugal today on a five-day
official goodwill visit to Greece.
</P>
<P>
Upon his arrival, Li said in a written statement that during his
visit, he will exchange views with Greek leaders on bilateral ties
and others issues of mutual concern.
