characters from a message written by President Jiang Zemin: "In
memory of Comrade Qiaomu".
</P>
<P>
The library opened a special reading room containing 16,000
books donated by Hu's family, in accordance with his final wishes.
</P>
<P>
Hu was born on June 1, 1912, and passed away in Beijing on
September 28, 1992. 
